{title: Send the Light}
{artist: Holly Dunn}
{composer: Written by Danny Zaloudik, Mike Speck, Goss Lari}

[C]There’s a call comes ringing o’er the restless wave
Send the light send the [G7]light
There are [C]souls to rescue there are souls to save
Send the light [G7]send the [C]light

Send the light the blessed gospel light
Let it [G7]shine from shore to [C]shore
Send the light the blessed gospel light
Let it [G7]shine forever [C]more

Let us pray that grace may everywhere abound
Send the light send the [G7]light
And a [C]Christ like spirit everywhere be found
Send the light [G7]send the [C]light
Repeat #2

Let us not grow weary in the work of love
Send the light send the [G7]light
Let us [C]gather jewels for a crown above
Send the light [G7]send the [C]light
Repeat #2 x2